{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"df0892d0-0d83-4f8c-bde9-8533904d1537","content":"**Yes, you will hit compatibility issues.** MSTest v3 dropped support for some of your target frameworks:\n\n- **`net5.0`** — ❌ Not supported. MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0+ (net5.0 reached end-of-life). You must upgrade to `net6.0` or later.\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — ❌ Not supported. Also end-of-life; upgrade to `net6.0`+.\n- **`net462`** — ⚠️ MSTest v3 requires at minimum **.NET Framework 4.6.2**, so this one is fine.\n\n### Recommended changes\n\nUpdate your `TargetFrameworks` to replace the unsupported TFMs:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFrameworks>net6.0;net462</TargetFrameworks>\n```\n\n(Or `net8.0` if you can target the latest LTS.)\n\nThen upgrade the MSTest packages to v3:\n\n```xml\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest.TestFramework\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest.TestAdapter\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />\n```\n\nWould you like me to perform the migration, or do you need more details on other MSTest v3 breaking changes (assertion API changes, timeout behavior, etc.)?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7483e0ea-00f3-49f4-98a6-542df39729fe","outputTokens":329,"requestId":"BC23:1EBB0A:206EA70:243C533:69FAA837"},"id":"d99f87f6-c5fc-4662-9231-ae48e8256ff7","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:32:31.056Z","parentId":"7e638090-a504-4b0c-b9a6-a3a590f83722"}
